{"tid":1449473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:57:43.000Z","uid":16567,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"24ef342eae25861afa6c745bd75107bb5e9895c4","tid":1449473,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=2667051d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=fd5ce850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"04ef7cfa15b9ed0d74e0e05c027d4b735d5b07c4","tid":1449473,"uid":100224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以同時set deadline<br />\n<br />\nDeadline後行動升級大罷工十日"},{"pid":"77c53cb50745f1de1e45a5ec56469bfdd9f341bf","tid":1449473,"uid":197331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78651046870e46fe5213c4153d72666c7a5f83c0","tid":1449473,"uid":112393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/